1. Introduction:

Welcome to Box Tower, a game developed and published by Activation Games. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the information we collect, how we use it, and your choices regarding your data. By using Box Tower, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect:

Personal Information:

We may collect and store your email address when you contact us for support or subscribe to newsletters. For example, you can reach out to us at activationgames4you@gmail.com.
Game Data:

Box Tower may collect non-personal information related to your gameplay, such as scores, achievements, and in-game progress. This information is used for improving the gaming experience.
Analytics:

We use Google Play Console analytics to gather data about how users interact with the game. This information helps us enhance the gameplay and fix issues.
3. How We Use Your Information:

Communication:

Your email address may be used for communication regarding support, updates, and promotional materials related to Box Tower.
Improvements:

We use the collected data to analyze and enhance the game's performance, features, and user experience.
Legal Compliance:

We may use your information to comply with legal obligations, such as responding to law enforcement requests.
4. Data Sharing:

Third-Party Services:

We may share non-personal information with third-party services, such as analytics providers, to help us understand and improve the game.
Legal Compliance:

We may disclose personal information if required by law or in response to a court order.
5. Your Choices:

Email Communications:

You can opt-out of receiving promotional emails by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the emails.
Analytics:

You can adjust your device settings to limit the collection of analytics data.
6. Security:

We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect, but no system can guarantee 100% security. Users are responsible for maintaining the security of their devices.
7. Children's Privacy:

Box Tower is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
8. Changes to the Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Changes will be effective when posted, and your continued use of Box Tower after the changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
9. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at activationgames4you@gmail.com.
By using Box Tower, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Thank you for choosing Box Tower!

